<p id="Par30" class="p">We detect long term annual NPP trend changes in every pixel by linear regression analysis. Existing research shows that the Greenness Rate of Change (GRC) can reflect the change trend of grassland NPP within a certain period of time
 <sup class="sup">
  <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR45" class="xref">45</xref>
 </sup>, following the equation (
 <xref rid="Equ8" ref-type="" class="xref">8</xref>):
